title: 2023 Summer Limited Edition GAN13 Maglev Coloré (For display only, not for sale)
Monster Go Magnetic 3x3 Cube
body_html:
• Affordable Magnetic Speed Cube - The Monster Go 3×3 magnet cube offers premium features at a budget-friendly price. With 48 magnets inside, it ensures consistently smooth turns. 
  • Exceptional Quality - Crafted from eco-friendly, Phthalate- and lead-free materials, each Monster Go cube is pre-lubed, tensioned, and rigorously tested before packaging. It’s a fantastic gift idea for kids and beginners eager to enter the world of speed cubing.

title: GAN356 X V2
body_html:
• Custom Magnet System - Gan 356 X v2 interchangeable magnet system allows all of the magnets to be changed in less than 30 seconds by hand. 
  • Dual Adjustment System - The GES Pro offers 4 kinds of nut distances and 6 tension settings. Fine-tune your cube quickly with just a tool and an alternate nut.
  • Precision Wing-Shaped Numerical Core -  GAN Wing-Shaped Numerical Core is lightweight and 100% vertical to six sides. Ensures perfect vertical alignment for greater stability
  • Built for Speed - Enjoy smooth turns, 55°/30° corner cutting, and anti-pop design. With honeycomb surfaces to reduce friction, this cube is made to break records.

title: GAN356 R S 2
body_html:
• 90° Full Corner Cutting - The GAN356 R S 2 boasts a 55°/30° corner-cutting ability that performs well with the toughest angles. Quickly move on to the next step; speeding up is effortless.
  • Customizable Tuning System - The 356 R S 2 has been updated with GES Pro+, featuring 3 centerpiece travel options and 4 tension options, helping you fine-tune your ideal feel.
  • Smooth and Lightweight Core - The GAN356 R S 2's new Wing-shaped Core 2.0 is designed for cuber enthusiasts. Offers a lighter feel while ensuring solid performance during fast and extended sessions.

title: GAN356 R S
body_html:
• Core and GES Upgrade - GAN356 R S features new Numerical Core and GES which makes the cube more stable and controllable, yet it can be easily tuned by hand.
  • Smooth and Stable - With honeycomb design on the corner contact points, GAN356 R S intended to create a smoother feel and prolong the life of lubricant.
  • Excellent Performance – GAN356 R S has 55°/ 30° corner-cutting ability that performs well with toughest angles. Seamless contact-surface with screw and snap joints is fall-apart friendly to the naughtiest kids.

title: Swift Block 355S Magnetic Cube
body_html:
• 48 Magnets for Precision and Speed - The Swift Block 355S 3×3 magnet speed cube features 48 visible magnets that guide each layer smoothly into place, enabling faster and more precise turns. 
  • Stable, Easy-to-Tune Construction - Equipped with a new numerical tension nut offering 5 adjustable settings, the Swift Block 355S provides remarkable stability. Its seamless contact surfaces, screw joints, and snap construction make it virtually unbreakable.

title: Swift Block wiSlide Klotski Slide Puzzle Game
body_html:
• Dive into the world of the Klotski puzzle with the innovative Swift Block WiSlide and the SlideVerse App. Embark on a journey of 1,000 in-app levels, challenge players around the world, and with a million challenges on the way in the online game pool, delivering endless opportunities for fun and mental exercise.
  • Enjoy smooth gameplay with real-time tracking, accurate movement detection, and an anti-cheat feature powered by high-precision magnetic sensors. With up to 15 hours of play per charge and adjustable brightness and volume, your gaming experience is fully customizable. Support for 6 languages opens this game to players worldwide.

title: Monster Go 251 Standard 2x2 Cube
body_html:
• Special Turning Feel - The Monster Go 2×2 cube is a fun, approachable puzzle with only 8 corners, making it simpler than the 3x3 cube but no less entertaining. With 3.6 million possible permutations, it’s full of exciting twists and turns that keep you engaged.
  • Safe and Smooth Design - This 2×2 cube is crafted from eco-friendly, stickerless plastic that’s Phthalate and lead-free, ensuring both a safe and comfortable experience. The smooth-turning mechanism provides an enjoyable, fluid feel with every move.

title: GAN356 i carry S Smart Cube
body_html: • An upgraded version of the beloved GAN356 i Carry, the i Carry S now features extended battery life—from 280 hours to 330 hours—for even more uninterrupted smart cubing. Whether you're practicing or battling online, enjoy longer sessions with the same trusted performance and intelligent features you love.

title: GAN356 Air M
body_html: The GAN356 Air M is only in stock and available for shipment to the following regions; please refrain from placing orders outside these areas: Austria / Belgium / Bulgaria / Czech Republic / Denmark / Finland / France / Germany / Greece / Hungary / Ireland / Italy / Lithuania / Luxembourg / Malta / Monaco / Netherlands / Norway / Poland / Portugal / Romania / San Marino / Slovenia / Slovakia / Spain / Sweden / United Kingdom. We apologize for any inconvenience caused.

title: GAN356 X S
body_html:
• SUPER LIGHTWEIGHT DESIGN - GAN356 X S is a product with all lightweight designs with only 67 grams, achieveing the lightest handfeels. 
  • SUPER STRAIGHTFORWARD ADJUSTMENT - It is equipped with 3 settings of mangets, 4 kinds of nut distances and 6 levels elasticity. All 72 configurations can be achieved within seconds.
  • SUPER STRUCTURAL MECHANISM - GAN Magnetic System(GMS) upgrades into GMS v2, with edge tabs to switch between 3 kind of magnetic force; GES Pro Dual Elasticity System is composed of dual numerical IPG core, GAN Tension Nut and numerical variable nut, to seperately fine control 6 kinds of elasticity and 4 kinds of nut distances.

title: GAN249 V2
body_html:
• The GAN249 features an innovative honeycomb design on its corner contact points, delivering a smoother feel and extending lubricant life. 
  • Equipped with GAN’s patented IPG core, this 2×2 speed cube offers improved turning that’s instantly noticeable while maintaining control. 
  • Weighing in at just 52 grams, the GAN249 V2 is exceptionally light. Its reduced weight enhances hand feel and boosts turning speed, making it a true speed booster in a compact form.

title: GAN330 Keychain
body_html:
• Solve It in Moments, Anytime, Anywhere - Enjoy endless entertainment with the GAN330 cube keychain—compact, accessible, and always ready for a quick solve.
  • Portable Cube Puzzle Toy - True to GAN’s signature quality, this mini cube keychain features impressive corner-cutting and smooth rotation, making it a fully functional puzzle that’s as portable as it is fun. Perfect for solving on the go!

title: GAN460 M Speed Cube
body_html:
• The GAN460 M redefines 4x4 speed cubing with its groundbreaking GMC (GAN Magnet Capsule) technology, showcasing 96 magnets securely locked within capsules. Offering unwavering reliability and power in every turn.
  • Engineered on a new 4x4 IPG core, combining iron and plastic for enhanced stability. Modeled after GAN’s iconic 3x3 IPG design, it offers higher perpendicularity, more internal space, and a longer hidden edge for superior anti-pop performance. This core structure provides strength and stability, setting a new standard in 4x4 speed cubes.
  • With optimized corner-cutting of 40°/25°, this cube incorporates all the latest features to help you shatter your personal best.

title: GAN356 M
body_html:
• A Cost-Effective Marvel - The GAN356 M delivers flagship-level features—plastic core, GES system, visible magnets, and anti-scratch surface—at a mid-range price for unbeatable value.
  • Unmatched Smoothness & Durability - An inner honeycomb design reduces friction and preserves lubrication, while classic corner feet provide superb corner cutting, anti-pop, and anti-twist capabilities. 
  • Effortless Tuning - The GAN356 M makes tuning easy with its GES+ (GAN Elastic System) design. With two adjustable distance slots, you can simply push and twist to adjust the tension. Set a looser feel with a larger distance and weaker elastic force, or tighten it up for a snappier response.

title: GAN356 Maglev
body_html:
• 30°+ Auto-Alignment Precision - 30°+ Auto-Alignment Precision - The GAN 356 Maglev’s magnetic force distribution grants over 30° of automatic alignment, ensuring each twist locks into place with accuracy and ease.
  • 36 Customization Options - With 6 elasticity levels and 6 center travel settings, the GAN 356 Maglev offers 36 different configurations. 
  • 76 Magnetic Points of Control - Dive into an advanced 3D magnetic environment, where 76 magnetic forces come together across the cube’s axes, edges, and corners. Each turn transforms into a controlled, floating motion that balances high energy with pinpoint accuracy.

title: GAN356 M E
body_html:
• Redefining Cubing Excellence - The GAN 356 M E upgrades the classic 356 M with Turbo Magnet Capsule 2.0, GES Pro+ tuning, and a wing-shaped core for smoother, faster, and more precise solving.
  • Magnetic Innovation - Equipped with 48 turbo magnet capsules, it offers strong positioning and acceleration for a high-speed, stable performance.
  • GES Pro+ Tuning System - Features 12 tension settings, 4 elasticity levels, and 3 axle distances—fully adjustable via a visible numerical system for easy, precise tuning.
  • Crafted for Endurance - The inner honeycomb design reduces friction, ensuring lubrication endures through countless solves.

title: GAN354 M
body_html: Now upgraded with a lightweight plastic core and tool-free numerical GES for precise tension tuning. At just 54mm, it’s perfect for one-handed solves and smaller hands. With 48 visible magnets and an airfoil Ganscore, each turn is smooth, stable, and accurate. The honeycomb design preserves lubrication, while anti-pop features ensure reliable speed. Small in size, big on performance—perfect for your next PB.

title: GAN251 V2
body_html:
• GAN251 v2: The Next Evolution in 2x2 Cubing - The new GAN251 v2 offers a larger size, a lighter frame, and an even smoother turning experience. 
  • Effortless Tuning with GES+ - Equipped with the latest GES+ technology, the GAN251 v2 brings noticeably improved turning dynamics while maintaining excellent control. Tuning is simple, allowing for a fully personalized cubing experience.
  • Ultra-Light, Ultra-Fast - Weighing in at just 47 grams, the GAN251 v2 is a featherweight powerhouse. This reduced weight enhances both hand feel and turning speed, offering an exceptional balance of comfort and speed.

title: GAN562 M
body_html:
• GAN 5x5 Cube: Breaking New Ground - Designed with omnidirectional core positioning and an innovative double-layer structure.
  • Omnidirectional Core Positioning - 16 internal magnetic particles paired with 96 external ones, driving optimal speed across 112 directions.
  • Double-Layer Design - Twice the Stability, Twice the Control. Lock corners, edges, and centers to prevent scattering, popping, and misalignments.
  • Turbo Magnet Capsules - Fully enclosed design where magnetic particles lock at 360°, preventing magnet loosening and ensuring long-term reliability.

title: GAN356 i carry 2 Smart Cube
body_html:
• A Pioneer in Smart Cubing - Seamlessly connecting to CubeStation for real-time battles, training, and tutorials—bringing the new smart cubing experience.
  • Extended Battery Life - Play without limits, thanks to a 700-hour battery life. Whether you’re at home or on the go, the GAN 356 iCarry 2 is ready whenever you are. 
  • Advanced Smart Ball Bearings - Equipped with non-contact magnetic induction, the 356 iCarry 2 activates with a simple shake. Its core has been reduced by 31.3% to minimize resistance, enhancing the smooth feel of each turn. A custom ball-bearing design further reduces external pressure and prevents jams.

title: GAN356 i 3 Smart Cube
body_html: Level up with the first Bluetooth cube featuring adjustable magnets. Choose from 7 magnetic strengths and 9 tension settings for a perfect feel. With Smart Core 3.0, enjoy ultra-precise tracking, gyroscope-based motion capture, and up to 15 hours of playtime. Join real-time global matches, improve with GAN AI Academy, and unlock exclusive rewards. Built to handle 50,000+ solves with 365-day standby—this is smart cubing at its best.

title: GAN251 M Series
body_html:
• What Makes The Differences - GAN 251 M Air has unadjustable corner magnets but no magnet in the core. That reduces the weight, and the cube turns very straightforward. Both Pro and Leap have the same corner core adjustable magnet system, and Leap has much bigger magnet in the core. Overall, two versions perform consistently good, Pro has better stability and Leap has faster speed.
  • Various Tuning - It is equipped with 2 kinds of nut distances, 4 levels elasticity, and optional 3 settings of magnets(Pro & Leap).

title: GAN356 i Carry Smart Cube
body_html:
• GAN356 i Carry: Smart, Affordable, Enduring - This 3x3 Bluetooth smart cube caters to both young beginners and seasoned speed cubers. Its replaceable battery offers an impressive 280 hours of playtime, delivering extended enjoyment without breaking the bank.
  • Real-Time Tracking - The GAN356 i Carry tracks four key stats—Time, Moves, Turns per Second (TPS), and Fluency—to give a comprehensive view of every solve.
  • Engineered for Speed and Precision - The GAN356 i Carry combines intelligence with high performance, weighing in at only 76 grams despite housing advanced sensors, a battery, and a circuit board. It also includes additional sets of springs and nuts for tailored tuning, catering to the preferences of competitive cubers.

title: GAN15 Maglev
body_html:
• Ultra-Lightweight at 58.6g - The GAN15 Maglev sets a new benchmark in 3×3 light speed cube engineering. Weighs about 58.6g. Its featherweight design responds to even the gentlest touch, allowing for effortless maneuverability.
  • Smooth Spherical Inner Track - Featuring a redesigned spherical inner track, every curve is precision-engineered, delivering a stable and silky-smooth rotation.
  • Upgraded GES V3 Structure - Featuring the GES V3 with secure safety clicks, the GAN15 Maglev keeps your tuning plate firmly locked. No more worries about parts shifting or popping out during solving.

title: GAN Cube Display Stand
body_html:
• COMPATIBLE MODELS - Fits GAN 3X3 smart puzzle cube and standard cubes: GAN icarry, GAN i3, GAN15 Maglev and so on.
  • UNIQUE STYLE - GAN cube display stand is a cube display stand that not only keeps GAN cube in a locked position but also makes the cube spin with a simple touch.
  • NEVER GET LOST - This display stand can hold gan cube tightly so that it will not easily fall out. The back of the adhesive tape can be attached firmly to any flat surface.
  • GOOD DECORATION - The stand is a great platform to show your cube. It can be placed anywhere in your home.
  • SAFER MATERIAL - Made of ABS material, GAN speed cube display is safe and odorless. It is environmentally friendly and healthy.

title: GAN12 Maglev
body_html:
• A NEW ERA WITH GAN12 - The GAN12 series, launched in 2021, continues the magnetic innovation. The GAN12 M Leap features GES Pro+ technology and weighs 61 grams, while the GAN12 Maglev uses the new Magnetic GES system at 66 grams. Both versions feature Enhanced Core Positioning 2.0, amplifying magnet strength and stability while reducing friction. The cubes are available in two exterior finishes: UV-Coated or Frosted.
  • MAGLEV TECHNOLOGY AND INNOVATION - The GAN12 Maglev introduces the next level of magnetic elasticity by replacing traditional springs with repelling magnets, mimicking the feel of springs while eliminating friction and noise. The result is an exceptionally smooth, stable experience that allows for lightning-fast solving right from the first turn.
  • AUTO-ALIGNMENT PRECISION - Upgraded to Enhanced Core Positioning 2.0, the GAN12 series extends magnets from the corners, enabling up to 30° auto-alignment. When the cube nears 30 degrees of a completed turn, it automatically aligns, giving you a fluid, effortless solving experience like never before.
  • EXPANDED CUSTOMIZATION OPTIONS - The GAN12 series takes customization to new heights, offering 6 levels of elasticity, 6 center travel options, and 7 levels of magnetic strength, resulting in 252 possible configurations. With this array of options, the GAN12 series can be tailored to suit your specific needs with ease. All accessories and step-by-step guides are provided for simple adjustments.
  • CONNECT WITH THE GAN FAMILY - By selecting GAN, you’re joining the world’s most successful 3x3 cube brand. Stay informed on the latest releases, connect with fellow cubers, and even provide feedback for future models. And don’t worry—GAN’s dedicated Customer Service Team is always ready to ensure your experience is nothing short of excellent.

title: GAN Speed Cube Cover - cube structure
GAN14 Maglev Pro
body_html:
• Enhanced Precision and Stability - The GAN14 Pro features refined edge pieces, advanced center-locking, and a secure latch system, delivering exceptional stability and alignment with effortless adjustments.
  • Consistent, Controlled Feel - With Enhanced Core Positioning 4.0 and 1296 configurations, it ensures even force distribution and customizable control for a balanced, responsive experience.
  • Magnetic Levitation Technology - A 12-setting maglev system offers near-frictionless turning and precise auto-alignment for smooth, fast performance.
  • Precision Tuning with Dual Adjustment - Provides 6 tension and 6 center travel options. This dual numerical system allows you to craft a cubing experience that’s entirely your own, offering a wide range of possibilities in one compact design.

title: GAN13 Maglev
body_html:
• DUAL MAGNETIC FORCE IN ACTION - For the first time, the GAN13 Maglev unites magnetic repulsion with magnetic attraction, a breakthrough in speed cube performance. 
  • ADVANCED CORE POSITIONING 3.0 - The GAN13 Maglev takes core positioning to a new level with repulsive magnets embedded in each of its 8 edge pieces, expanding the maglev area and enhancing speed. Inside, 88 precision-placed magnets provide balanced magnetic force, delivering a remarkably stable and fluid feel.
  • EXCEPTIONAL NUMERICAL TUNING OPTIONS - Customization reigns supreme in the GAN13 series. With 6 elasticity levels, 6 center travel settings, and 6 levels of magnet strength, you can explore 216 possible configurations to fine-tune your cube’s performance.

title: GAN Halo Smart Timer
body_html:
• Connecting to APP---Smart recording, analyzing and practicing.
  • Offline Result Storing---smart phone & PC free
  • Auto Counting AO5---Farewll to manual calculating.
  • Halo Light System---Light customization and 90 sets of light effects.
  • Cross-platform Storing---No data losing.
  • All in One---Clear operation.

title: GAN14 Maglev
body_html:
• GAN 2023 Flagship: 1296 Unique Configurations - Continuing its tradition of excellence from GAN 12 to the latest GAN 14 Maglev, GAN redefines the standard in cubing innovation. The GAN14 M is equipped with 1296 unique configuration options, allowing you to refine each turn to achieve the ideal feel. This flagship model epitomizes GAN’s commitment to advanced cubing.
  • Sophisticated Corner-Edge Magnet System - The GAN14 Maglev raises the bar with its intricate, fully adjustable magnetic setup. Featuring three levels of magnetic strength across corner, center, and edge pieces, it allows for comprehensive fine-tuning. This design minimizes friction and resistance, ensuring a seamless, high-performance experience with every twist.
  • Precision Numerical Tuning System - Designed for customization, this magnetic cube offers 12 distinct magnet adjustments, supporting precise turns between 15 and 40 degrees. With a user-friendly 3D tool for magnet replacement and a GES v3 dual tuning system, the cube provides 6 tension settings and 6 center travel adjustments, opening a world of possibilities to craft your perfect feel.
  • Enhanced Core Positioning 4.0 - Leveraging 88 strategically positioned magnets, the GAN14 M uses Core Positioning 4.0 technology. With 12 magnetic strengths at corners and 3 at edges, the cube achieves a balanced magnetic pull. Each twist is elevated by this powerful magnetic layout, delivering unparalleled smoothness across 1296 configuration possibilities.
  • GAN Certification and Community - Choosing GAN means choosing a globally recognized brand, synonymous with cubing excellence. With GAN, you’ll access the latest innovations, engage with an enthusiastic community of cubers, and stay at the forefront of cubing technology. GAN’s Customer Service Team ensures a seamless experience, offering full support and assistance every step of the way.

title: GAN Skewb M
body_html: Weighing just 79g, the GAN Skewb is the lightest skewb on the market, featuring built-in core magnets for fast, stable turns. Its Magnetic Core-Positioning System ensures precise alignment, while the GES Pro dual adjustment offers 24 tuning options for a customized feel. With 90° corner cutting, a smooth track design, and a durable stickerless finish, it delivers a top-tier solving experience.

title: GAN Pyraminx M
body_html: The GAN Pyraminx M is the lightest Pyraminx on the market at just 64g, built for speed and effortless control. It features a triple magnetic system with 60 embedded magnets across the core, edges, and centers for smooth, precise turns. The Magnetic Core Positioning ensures fast alignment and low resistance, while the GES+ system offers four sets of elastic nuts for easy, customizable tension. With 120° corner cutting, honeycomb touchface, anti-lock design, and a durable stickerless finish, it delivers a top-tier solving experience.
